contentrichtext.text: '''WI''' may refer to: * [[Wisconsin]] United States postal abbreviation * [[Wiesbaden]], a city in southwest Germany * [[Netflix#Internet video streaming|Watch Instantly]], a video streaming service offered by Netflix * [[Ice Climbing#Waterfall ice grading|Waterfall Ice]], the ice formed from a frozen waterfall * [[West Indies]] postal abbreviation ** [[West Indies cricket team]], a term used in cricket statistics * [[Women's Institutes]], a locally organised group for British women '''Wi''' may refer to: * [[Wi (kana)]], an obsolete Japanese character * [[Wi (mythology)]], a Lakota deity * [[Wi, Inc.]], an American medical device development corporation * [[Wiman (disambiguation)|Wiman]], [[Europe|European]] surname * [[Wi Man of Gojoseon]], ruler of [[Wiman Joseon]] * Wi, common of surname [[Wei (disambiguation)|Wei]] (魏, 韋, 衛, 尉) ==See also== * [[Wii]], Nintendo's fifth home video game console * [[W1 (disambiguation)]] {{disambiguation}}
